# Responsive Device Fit (300 Awakening)

Every page and component must adapt cleanly from small phones ‚Üí large phones ‚Üí tablets ‚Üí desktop browsers ‚Üí Capacitor iOS/Android.

## Shell pattern (default for dashboard + flows)

Wrap interactive pages in a centered mobile-first shell:

```tsx
<main className="min-h-dvh w-full bg-[#0B090A] pt-safe pb-safe text-white">
  <div className="mx-auto flex min-h-dvh w-full max-w-md flex-col px-4 sm:px-6 md:max-w-lg lg:max-w-xl">
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</main>
```

- **Mobile:** full width, edge-to-edge content inside shell padding
- **Desktop:** centered column (`mx-auto`), never stretch UI beyond `max-w-md`‚Äì`max-w-xl`
- Intro/splash routes may be **full-bleed** (`w-full h-dvh`) with no shell ‚Äî exception only for cinematic routes

## Viewport & height

- Prefer `min-h-dvh` / `h-dvh` over `min-h-screen` (fixes mobile browser chrome)
- Root layout already sets `viewportFit: cover` ‚Äî always use `pt-safe` and `pb-safe` on page roots
- Never use fixed `px` heights for full-page layouts; use `dvh`, `%`, or `flex-1`

## Media (video, images, artwork)

```tsx
className="h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
```

- Hero/video: `object-cover`; avoid letterboxing unless intentional
- Use `aspect-video` or `h-[50dvh]` for player regions, not fixed pixel heights
- Images: always `w-full`, `max-w-full`, `h-auto` or `object-cover` inside bounded containers

## Typography & touch targets

- Body: `text-sm sm:text-base`; headings scale with `text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl`
- Buttons/inputs: minimum `py-3 px-4`; pill rows use `overflow-x-auto` + `shrink-0` for horizontal scroll
- Uppercase labels: `text-xs tracking-[0.2em]` ‚Äî do not shrink below `text-[0.6rem]` on mobile

## Layout rules

- Use `flex` / `grid` ‚Äî never absolute positioning for primary content flow
- Horizontal strips: `flex gap-2 overflow-x-auto` with `min-w-max` inner wrapper
- Sticky footers: `mt-auto` inside flex column + `pb-safe`
- Modals/drawers: `fixed inset-x-0 bottom-0 mx-auto max-w-md` (match shell width)

## Forbidden

- Fixed widths like `w-[375px]` for page containers
- `100vh` without `dvh` fallback on full-screen pages
- Desktop-only layouts that break below `320px` width
- Horizontal overflow on `body` (test at 320px and 428px)

## Checklist before shipping UI

1. Renders at 320px wide without horizontal scroll
2. Safe areas respected on notched devices (`pt-safe` / `pb-safe`)
3. Desktop shows centered shell, not stretched full-width forms
4. Tap targets ‚â• 44px effective height
